Annotation Type FieldBuilder.CheckBoxGroup


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=METHOD)
 @Documented
public static @interface FieldBuilder.CheckBoxGroup
    Specifies how a Java property should be edited using an CheckBoxGroup.
    See Also:
    FieldBuilder.AbstractMultiSelect, FieldBuilder
